  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Role:</strong> Striker. You concentrate on either ranged attacks or two-weapon melee fighting to deal a lot of damage to one enemy at a time. Your attacks rely on speed and mobility, since you prefer to use hit-andrun tactics whenever possible.</p><p><strong>Power Source: </strong>Martial. Your talents depend on extensive training and practice, inner confidence, and natural proficiency</p><p><strong>Key Abilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Strength</p></li><li><p>Dexterity</p></li><li><p>Wisdom</p></li></ul><p><strong>Armour Proficiencies:</strong></p><ul><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.equipmentPack.Item.GwsMGFG3ogxFrvmJ]{Cloth armor (basic clothing)}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.equipmentPack.Item.lnYMh2YvKedWTpCt]{Leather armor}</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.equipmentPack.Item.kVD04UqK9Yx6GeRA]{Hide armor}</p></li></ul><p><strong>Weapon Proficiencies:</strong></p><ul><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\"><p>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.srd_rules.JournalEntry.p9xY7n4f0uabD02e.JournalEntryPage.kjW9S8gIQ0LBMF53]{Simple Melee Weapons}</p></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\"><p>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.srd_rules.JournalEntry.p9xY7n4f0uabD02e.JournalEntryPage.ezGAD5rtV5TLGhDQ]{Military Melee Weapons}</p></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\"><p>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.srd_rules.JournalEntry.p9xY7n4f0uabD02e.JournalEntryPage.G50MDDGV8v1NRT9u]{Simple Ranged Weapons}</p></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\"><p>@UUID[Compendium.dnd4e.srd_rules.JournalEntry.p9xY7n4f0uabD02e.JournalEntryPage.X6ukbUgTQolHx7PO]{Military Ranged Weapons}</p></li></ul><p><strong>Bonus to Defences:</strong></p><ul><li><p>+1 Fortitude</p></li><li><p>+1 Reflex</p></li></ul><p><strong>Hit Points at 1st Level:</strong> [[12]] + Con Score</p><p><strong>Hit Points per Level Gained:</strong> [[5]]</p><p><strong>Base Healing Surges per Day:</strong> [[6]] + Con Mod</p><p><strong>Skill Training:</strong> Dungeoneering or Nature, choose four more from the following list:</p><ul><li><p>Acrobatics (Dex)</p></li><li><p>Athletics (Str)</p></li><li><p>Endurance (Con)</p></li><li><p>Healing (Wis)</p></li><li><p>Perception (Wis)</p></li><li><p>Stealth (Dex)</p></li></ul><p><strong>Class Features:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Hunter's Quarry</p></li><li><p>Prime Shot</p></li></ul><p><strong>Choose one of the following Fighting Style:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Archer Fighting Style</p></li><li><p>Two-Blade Righting Style</p></li></ul>",
